text: Pascal Potié (born 15 March 1964) is a French former cyclist. He competed at the 1984, 1988 and 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:People from Seclin Category:French male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of France Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:French track cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Nord (French department)
